data.description:
Step into your new sanctuary. This remarkable Carothers home showcases a spacious layout. As you enter, be greeted by the inviting living room, with the focal point of a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace. The kitchen features exquisite quartz countertops complemented by white cabinets and a tasteful tile backsplash. Discover the comfort of this home's three cozy bedrooms with a bathroom in the hall on the opposite side of the home.  Experience the cutting convenience of a smart home with an array of amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle. Experience fast connectivity with the advanced 100GB ethernet wiring throughout the home. HDMI wiring in the master bedroom, living room, and converted garage. This will allow for a seamless integration of your entertainment systems. This home is equipped with smart technology that seamlessly integrates with popular voice assistants such as Amazon Alexa, Google Voice, and Siri. Control your lights with ease using smart light switches. Stay connected and secure with a doorbell camera and cameras around the house. Enjoy the convenience of smart electrical plugs. Finally elevate your living space with smart electronic window shades, allowing you to effortlessly adjust natural light and privacy levels with a simple voice command or touch of a button. Embrace the comforts of home automation and make everyday living a breeze.
Roof replaced 2 yrs ago and hot water heater replaced last year.
